<plot>On a dreary January 19, 2002, in Newport, Tennessee, the Ku Klux Klan held a pre-announced rally on the courthouse steps. 'a rainy day in january' focuses primarily on the voices that spoke that stressful day at the community's annual Diversity Festival, highlighting the town's spirit rising to overcome the past, again.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?015152</url></doc>
